div.head: Estonian Attribute Index
div.p: In this section all the attributes presented in the tables are listed in alphabetical order.

div.head: Estonian Value Index
Estonian MSD Index
div.p: This index gives the liist of morphosyntactic descriptions (MSDs) and their features. In the table below, the first column gives the MSD, the second its expansion into a feature-structure, the third gives the number of entries in the lexicon (135,094 entries), and the fourth gives some examples as word-form/lemma. The list was extracted form the Estonian MULTEXT-East lexicon.
